data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This move-in ready 4-bedroom, 3-bath rambler. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere and an abundance of natural light flooding through the windows. The living room provides the ideal setting for relaxation or entertaining guests with a cozy fireplace to gather around on chilly evenings.   Downstairs, the fully finished basement provides even more living space, with a family room that's perfect for movie nights or game days. Need office space and a separate access for a business? This home offers rooms for a family or for a home business. A full bathroom adds convenience and bedroom in the basement rounds out this great basement.  Outside, you'll discover your own deck overlooking the fenced backyard. An extra storage room under the deck for your equipment. With a large carport and a generator plug for added convenience, this home has everything you need and more
